description=Tests for genes for which there is evidence of expression spatial gradients with respect to a \"reference\" tissue niche/domain (e.g., higher expression closer to reference tissue niche, lower expression as farther from reference tissue niche).
documentationUrl=https://genepattern.github.io/spatialGE.STgradient/v1/
